overview.en: SEDA focuses on creating an ecosystem to facilitate an on demand, secure, verified (REAL & TRUE) and rewarding mechanism for participating parties in the ecosystem - where accreditations and credentials are being verified on the Blockchain.
overview.zh: SEDA专注于创建一个通过使用区块链来供应安全和被验证的生态系统，并为参与者提供奖励机制
